{"id":232832066,"title":"#請益 輕便的相機(內有選手)","content":"最近想買部相機去旅行拍影片\n因為要顧小孩，所以不方便拿太重的相機\n以下幾部是我看完資料後覺得很合適的，但選不下手，因為好像各有各好，希望大家能給意見🙏🏻\n我主要想要翻屏/小螢幕可以看到自己的\n可以加收音麥，小巧方便\n\n一號選手Sony RX100 M7 黑卡\nhttps://i.imgur.com/ll6SuGf.jpg\n這部相比其他相機算小，但好像不防手震？\n\n二號選手dji osmo pocket\nhttps://i.imgur.com/cvRAqjj.jpg\n這部一直很想買，但看評價好像缺點蠻多的，一直等第二代，結果還沒有消息\n\n三號選手sony RX0 M2\nhttps://i.imgur.com/rQr587O.jpg\n這部很小很方便，但聽說對焦不友好\n螢幕太小、也看不清到底有沒有對焦\n\n這三部一直都選不下，好像都有缺點\n如果有其他小巧相機的話也可以推薦\n價錢不過3萬都可以\n謝謝大家","excerpt":"最近想買部相機去旅行拍影片，因為要顧小孩，所以不方便拿太重的相機，以下幾部是我看完資料後覺得很合適的，但選不下手，因為好像各有各好，希望大家能給意見，我主要想要翻屏/小螢幕可以看到自己的，可以加收音麥","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d0cd5819-4627-4b5f-8a8e-050976e0fba1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-05T15:41:41.113Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-05T15:41:41.113Z","commentCount":13,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["攝影","旅遊"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"攝影","forumAlias":"photography","school":"香港城市大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/ll6SuGf.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/cvRAqjj.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/rQr587O.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c5df42a8-f29f-46a5-a641-78ff1fa0602d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/ll6SuGfl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/ll6SuGfl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/ll6SuGfl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-05T15:41:41.113Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-05T15:41:41.113Z"},{"id":"c5df42a8-f29f-46a5-a641-78ff1fa0602d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/ll6SuGf.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/ll6SuGf","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/ll6SuGfl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2